release.changelog: In this update, a button has been added to the browser menu to translate websites that are not displayed in your device's language using Google Translate. Additionally, the previous URL system has been restored. Now, when you close the browser with a website open, you will resume from the previous web page upon returning. We have also made some minor changes to improve your browsing experience.
